    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <img class="h-full w-full object-contain" src="{{dumpster_image}}" alt="">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-old-standard text-3xl font-bold text-[#0016A2] mb-2">Why work with our company?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6">By choosing Alpha Junk Removal & Services to haul your junk, you'll be partnering with a company who aims to put its customers first on every job. We don't believe the job is done until you are completely satisfied. You can rest easy knowing that we:</p>
          <ul class="mb-6 text-lg space-y-1 lg:pl-16">
            <li class="before:icon-image-[material-symbols--task-alt-rounded] before:[mask-image:--svg] before:[mask-repeat:no-repeat] before:[mask-size:contain] before:h-5 before:w-5 before:mr-2 before:text-[#0016A2] before:bg-[currentColor] flex items-center">Offer competitive pricing on fast service</li>
            <li class="before:icon-image-[material-symbols--task-alt-rounded] before:[mask-image:--svg] before:[mask-repeat:no-repeat] before:[mask-size:contain] before:h-5 before:w-5 before:mr-2 before:text-[#0016A2] before:bg-[currentColor] flex items-center">Have years of experience in the industry</li>
            <li class="before:icon-image-[material-symbols--task-alt-rounded] before:[mask-image:--svg] before:[mask-repeat:no-repeat] before:[mask-size:contain] before:h-5 before:w-5 before:mr-2 before:text-[#0016A2] before:bg-[currentColor] flex items-center">Provide free estimates on every job</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-lg">If you need a dependable team to haul away your junk, we're ready to help you. Make us your go-to junk removal company.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% set bg_image_3 = theme.path ~ '/assets/images/bg_image_3.jpg' %}
  <div class="bg-[#0016A2] py-32 text-white text-center relative">
    <div aria-hidden="true" class="h-full w-full object-cover opacity-20 absolute z-0 inset-0 bg-cover" style="background-image:url('{{bg_image_3}}')"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto relative z-10 px-4">
      <div class="mx-auto space-y-5">
        <div class="max-w-5xl">
          <h2 class="font-old-standard text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-center">Offering compassionate services during your time of loss</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-4xl space-y-5">
          <p class="text-lg">Handling an estate cleanout on your own is emotionally and physically taxing. Let Alpha Junk Removal & Services help. We offer professional estate cleanout services in Grand Island, NY and the Western NY area.</p>
          <p class="text-lg">We'll work hard to make the estate cleanout process as stress-free as possible while you grieve. You can even count on us to sweep and vacuum up afterward, so you won't have to worry about a thing.</p>
          <p class="text-lg">Lean on our team of courteous, trained professionals. Schedule your estate cleanout service in Grand Island, NY and the Western NY area today.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
{% endblock content %}
